name: Artificial Inu
description: Artificial Inu ($AI) is where memes meet machine learning. Combining the viral charm of meme tokens with cutting-edge AI, $AI introduces a new kind of Inu' one that thinks, adapts, and interacts. Backed by a smart, evolving mascot and fueled by community creativity, the project offers AI-generated content, meme creation tools, and interactive experiences. It’s not just another dog coin, it’s a tech-forward, laughter-filled ride into the future of Web3 engagement. Artificial Inu proves that even memes can be intelligent.
